{"id":232976627,"title":"學店分類","content":"小弟看到dcard上戰校戰來戰去的，其中最熱鬧的就是學店和非學店的爭論，於是我代替孔子來為學店分類，不認同的還請分享一下各位的意見。\n首先，常常有人提到學店邏輯，到底什麼是學店邏輯？\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/9b055043-ed4e-4b61-b5ce-88ac2f16e48b/1280.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/ffd0f775-72a2-4c20-9c58-23dddda3d1f1/1280.jpeg\n———————————————————————\n結論：台清交成政以外都學店，可能有人會說我標準太嚴，可是我在高二的時候連判別式都不會，第一次模考還考20多級分最後還不是一樣考得上台大，其實只要認真讀書，不可能連五大都考不上（醫學系的不算在學店）。說那麼多，其實很多都只是店生的藉口而已，與其狡辯，不如多花時間充實自己吧\n\n補個：其實戰校也沒什麼意義，只要自己喜歡就好了，沒必要去管別人怎樣，這篇文的意義主要是分類學店，並不是要大家互相戰校喔，謝謝各位，顆顆","excerpt":"小弟看到dcard上戰校戰來戰去的，其中最熱鬧的就是學店和非學店的爭論，於是我代替孔子來為學店分類，不認同的還請分享一下各位的意見。首先，常常有人提到學店邏輯，到底什麼是學店邏輯？——————————","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"255fd275-fec2-49d2-8e46-2e1557ffaeb0","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-29T05:41:34.947Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-29T05:41:34.947Z","commentCount":35,"likeCount":0,"tags":[],"topics":["學店","學店悲歌","學店生"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"閒聊","forumAlias":"talk","school":".","department":"tunghenglee","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/9b055043-ed4e-4b61-b5ce-88ac2f16e48b/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/ffd0f775-72a2-4c20-9c58-23dddda3d1f1/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"7be86978-2a2c-4d5b-92d0-870e1cea223d","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/9b055043-ed4e-4b61-b5ce-88ac2f16e48b/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/9b055043-ed4e-4b61-b5ce-88ac2f16e48b/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/9b055043-ed4e-4b61-b5ce-88ac2f16e48b/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":[],"createdAt":"2020-01-29T05:41:34.947Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-29T05:41:34.94